===Etymology===
:'''Screwdriver''': From english [[screw]] + english [[driver]]

===Noun===
#A tool which engages with the head of a [[screw]] and allows [[torque]] to be applied to turn the screw, thus driving it in or loosening it.
#A drink made of vodka and orange juice.

